arStrings.szText: My dearest friend, you refused to listen to reason, so I decided for us both.
The Loom is dead. You will find the tunnels collapsed, the siphons broken, and the runes scoured. To rebuild it without me would take a lifetime.

I hope you realize your mistake. I hope you abandon this dream, as I have. I hope you join the Horadrim with me. And if none of that comes to pass, I hope you live well. 
-Zoltun
